com.tozny.e3db

Class RecordData

  • Object
    • com.tozny.e3db.RecordData

  • public class RecordData
extends Object
    Specifies the unencrypted data for a record.

    This class is only used when creating a record via Client.write(String, RecordData, Map, ResultHandler) or updating an existing record using Client.update(RecordMeta, RecordData, Map, ResultHandler)).
